      This falls into the same category as a similar idea entered elsewhere on this web site, i.e.,  of "telling the truth" in all areas and not just in science. And one can only tell the truth if one knows the truth - and this is tricky. Even in scienec it is often that an opinion is expressed, an interpretation of data that is later changed... <br/>Let's put honesty into every aspect of this new, future eGovernment!

                  
